    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/92775a4bcaff455968d008f1c2163adc.poster.avif?t=1705872729\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/92775a4bcaff455968d008f1c2163adc.webm?t=1705872729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/92775a4bcaff455968d008f1c2163adc.mp4?t=1705872729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>ExtermiHate is a top down twin stick shooter action rogue-lite where you play as Raven &quot;Luna&quot; Ticke. She is a lone prisoner-turned-soldier sent in to reclaim Earth  from a bug invasion. Fight your way through random levels and level up your character to survive the waves and defeat the bosses.<br><br> Shortly after re-terraforming it we found out what lurked beneath. Forced to leave and regroup we are now ready to go back and fight for our new home. The issue is the powers that be only want to send criminals to do their dirty work.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/e939b22255e148d1cc60e46d18fa79ac.poster.avif?t=1705872729\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/e939b22255e148d1cc60e46d18fa79ac.webm?t=1705872729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234740/extras/e939b22255e148d1cc60e46d18fa79ac.mp4?t=1705872729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You play as Raven Luna Ticke. One of the last ex-military criminals just crazy enough to be a one-woman-army and kill every last overgrown bug stopping humanity from taking over the planet.<br><br>Fight your way through multiple random maps with different modes like Wave and Kill All to succeed in reclaiming the planet.",
